          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "法也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-32",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 30,
          "end": 48
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "古贍字蔡邕獨斷曰漢天子正號曰皇帝自稱曰朕臣民稱之曰陛下陛階也所由升堂也天子必有近臣執兵陳於陛側以戒不虞謂之陛下者羣臣與天子言不敢指斥天子故呼在陛下者而告之因卑逹尊之意也上書亦如之及羣臣士庻相與言曰殿下閤下執事之屬皆此類也元元庻民也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-33",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 48,
          "end": 61
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音披",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-34",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "祭公謀父曰先王耀徳不觀兵是故周文公之頌曰載戢干戈載櫜弓矢我求懿徳肆于時夏允王保之先王之於民也茂正其徳而厚其性阜其財而利其器用明利害之鄉以文修之使之務利而辟害懷徳而畏威故能保世以滋大兵畧訓曰湯之七十里而王者修徳也智伯有千里之地而亡者窮武也故千里之國行文徳者王萬乗之國好用兵者亡",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-35",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 15,
          "end": 50
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音絮",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-36",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 55
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "食貨志曰自神農之世斵木為耜揉木為耒耒耜之利以教天下而食足日中為市致天下之民聚天下之貨交易而退各得其所而貨通食足貨通然後國實民富而教化成黄帝以下通其變使民不倦李奇曰器幣有不便於時則變更通利之使民樂其業而不倦也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-37",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 55,
          "end": 84
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "吕氏春秋曰農攻粟工攻器賈攻貨時事不共是謂大凶周書曰農不出則乏其食工不出則乏其事商不出則三寳絕虞不出則財匱少財匱少而山澤不辟矣此四者民所衣食之原也原大則饒原小則鮮上則富國下則富家",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-38",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 62
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "釋名曰躁燥也如物燥則飛揚賈逵曰躁擾也淮南齊俗訓曰亂國若盛治國若虚亡國若不足存國若有餘虚者非無人也皆守其職也盛者非多人也皆徼於末也有餘者非多財也欲節事寡也不足者非無貨也民躁而費多也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-39",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 62,
          "end": 74
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "古防字",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-40",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 61
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音南",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-41",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 61,
          "end": 93
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "貨殖傳曰夫山西饒材竹穀纑旄玉石山東多魚鹽漆絲聲色江南出柟梓薑桂金錫連丹沙犀瑇瑁珠璣齒革龍門碣石北多馬牛羊旃裘筋角銅鐡則千里徃徃山出綦置皆中國人民所喜好謡俗被服飲食奉生送死之具也故待農而食之虞而出之工而成之商而通之此寕有政教發徴期會哉人各任其能竭其力以得所欲故物賤之徴貴貴之徵賤各勸其業樂其事若水之趨下日夜無休時不召而自來不求而民出之豈非道之所符而自然之驗耶",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-42",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 93,
          "end": 125
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "易曰黄帝堯舜垂衣裳而天下治蓋取諸乾坤刳木為舟剡木為楫舟楫之利以濟不通盖取諸渙服牛乗馬引重致逺以利天下盖取諸隨",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-43",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 125,
          "end": 134
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "古瞻字",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-44",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 48
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "管子曰國有十年之畜而民不足於食是皆以其技能望君之禄也君有山海之金而民不足於用是皆以其事業交接於其上也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-45",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 48,
          "end": 61
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "古贍字",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-46",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 61,
          "end": 63
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "汜論曰𩅸水足以溢壺榼江河不能實漏巵王符曰山林不能給野火江海不能實漏巵",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-47",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 63,
          "end": 73
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "殷紀曰帝盤庚之時殷已都河北盤庚渡河南復居成湯之故居乃五遷無定處殷民咨胥皆怨不欲徙盤庚乃告諭諸侯大臣曰昔髙后成湯與爾之先祖俱定天下法則可修舍而弗勉何以成徳乃遂渉河南治亳行湯之政然後百姓由寧殷道復興諸侯來朝以其遵成湯之徳也泰族訓曰夫水出於山而入於海稼生於田而藏於倉聖人見其所生則知其所歸矣故舜深藏黄金於蔪巖之山所以塞貪鄙之心也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-48",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 73,
          "end": 78
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音古",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-49",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 78,
          "end": 96
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "食貨志曰秦兼天下幣為二等黄金以鎰為名上幣銅錢質如周錢文曰半兩重如其文而珠玉龜貝銀錫之屬為器飾寳藏不為幣然各隨時而輕重漢興以為秦錢重難用更令民鑄筴錢黄金一斤而不軌逐利之民畜積餘贏以稽市物痛騰躍米至石萬錢馬至四百金天下已平高祖乃令賈人不得衣絲乗車重稅租以困辱之孝惠高后時為天下初定復弛商賈之律然市井子孫亦不得官為吏顔師古曰欲令務農也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-50",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 96,
          "end": 100
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "排斥也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-51",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 100,
          "end": 101
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "古防字",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-52",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 101,
          "end": 117
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "去聲",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-53",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 117,
          "end": 121
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "去聲",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-54",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 121,
          "end": 138
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "劉向曰周天子使家父毛伯求金於諸侯春秋譏之故天子好利則諸侯貪諸侯貪則大夫鄙大夫鄙則庻人盗上之變下猶風之靡草也故為人君者明貴徳而賤利以道下下之為惡尚不可止今隐公貪利而身自漁濟上而行八佾以此化於國人國人安得不解於義解於義而縱其欲則災害起而臣下僻矣故其元年始書⿰虫𡨋言災害將起國家將亂云爾司馬遷曰余讀孟子書至梁惠王問何以利吾國未嘗不廢書而歎也曰嗟乎利誠亂之始也夫子罕言利者常防其原也故曰放於利而行多怨自天子至於庶人好利之𡚁何以異哉",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-55",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 138,
          "end": 145
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "管子曰利出於一孔者其國無敵出二孔者其兵不詘出三孔者不可以舉兵出四孔者其國必亡先王知其然故塞民之養隘其利途故予之在君介之在君貧之在君富之在君故民之戴上如日月親君若父母梯階也詩曰無拳無勇職為亂階",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-56",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 59
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "籠包舉也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-57",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 59,
          "end": 72
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "如淳曰縣官天子也張晏曰不敢斥言天子謂之縣官也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-58",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 72,
          "end": 74
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音古",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-59",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 74,
          "end": 78
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "如淳曰牟取也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-60",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音工",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-61",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 29,
          "end": 32
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "食貨志曰古者民受田有賦有稅賦供車馬兵甲士徒之役充實府庫賜予之用稅給郊社宗廟百神之祀天子奉養百官禄食庶事之費周禮曰司稼掌廵邦野之稼而辨穜稑之種周知其民與其所宜地以為法而縣于邑閭廵野觀稼以年之上下出歛法掌均萬民之食而賙其急而平其興典婦功掌婦式之法以授嬪婦及内人女功之事齎凡授嬪婦功及秋獻功辨其苦良比其小大而賈之物書而揭之以供王及后之用頒之于内府",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-62",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 32,
          "end": 52
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音諫",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-63",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 52,
          "end": 57
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "平聲使令也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-64",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 57,
          "end": 98
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "平聲",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-65",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 98,
          "end": 101
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音工",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-66",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 101,
          "end": 112
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音委",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-67",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 112,
          "end": 130
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "司馬貞曰騰躍者謂物踊貴而價起有如物之騰躍而起也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-68",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 130,
          "end": 135
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音古",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-69",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 135,
          "end": 139
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "行貨曰商坐販曰賈",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-70",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 139,
          "end": 161
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音古",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-71",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 161,
          "end": 191
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "去聲",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-72",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
